query:
SELECT 
  v.id, 
  v.valorTotal, 
  v.dataVenda,
  v.updatedAt,
  f.nome as formandoNome,
  t.codigo as turmaCodigo
FROM vendas v
JOIN formandos f ON v.formandoId = f.id
JOIN turmas t ON f.turmaId = t.id
WHERE f.nome LIKE '%Mayara%' AND f.nome LIKE '%Vasconcelos%' AND t.codigo = '902';
